Commission on Health and Safety and Workers' Compensation, Hyatt Regency, San
Francisco, 415-557-1304.

Apr 21-26 - 34th Annual Risk & Insurance Management Society Inc. conference,
Metro Toronto Convention Center, Toronto, 212-286-9292.

Apr 28-May 1, 1996 - Eighth Annual National Managed Health Care Congress,
Washington Convention Center, Washington, DC 617-270-6000.




