WR BERKLEY/SIGNET STAR

WR Berkley Corp (WRBC), Greenwich CT, has increased its ownership of
Signet Star Holdings Inc, Basking Ridge NJ, to 100% through the
purchase of a 40% stake from General Re Corp, Stamford CT (WICR173/17).
 WRBC issued 450,000 shares of preferred stock to General Re valued at
about US$68.8m.  WRBC also guaranteed a senior subordinated promissory
note of Signet Star Holdings in the principal amount of $35.8m, which
matures on 1 July 2003 and bears interest at a rate of 6.5%.



