January 12, 1996

ZURICH/KEMPER

Zurich Versicherungs-Gruppe, Zurich, and Insurance Partners have
completed the acquisition of Kemper Corp, Long Grove IL, in a
transaction valued at slightly more than US$2bn (WICR170/22).



