PEOPLE'S BANKCORP GRANTED INSURANCE LICENCE

People's Bankcorp Inc of Marietta OH has been granted a licence by the
Ohio insurance department to distribute life, motor and property
insurance through a wholly-owned insurance agency, provided that
insurance activity is physically separated from banking activity in its
branches, the majority of policies are sold to non-customers of the
bank, and customers are not required to buy insurance from the bank for
any reason.  The licence is opposed by the Independent Insurance Agents
of  Ohio, which will challenge its validity in court.



