LLOYD'S INVESTMENT TRUSTS RULING

Following discussions between the Lloyd's Corporate Capital Association
and the Inland Revenue, the latter said that it has no objection in
principle to confirming investment trust status for corporate capital
vehicles provided that they meet the normal criteria for investment
trusts.  No corporate vehicle has yet had its investment trust status
confirmed, however.



